  "instructions": [
    "1. Rinse and dry the cauliflower florets.",
    "2. In a bowl, mix together festive oil, garlic, cumin, lime juice, pepper powder, and salt.",
    "3. Add the cauliflower florets to the bowl and toss to coat with the sauce.",
    "4. Heat a skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "5. Add the cauliflower florets to the skillet and cook until crispy and golden brown.",
